body:
``` bash
git checkout master && git fetch upstream && git merge upstream/master
make clean
make
hack/update-codecgen.sh 
codecgen error: error running 'go run codecgen-main-1234.generated.go': exit status 2, console: # _/home/deads/workspaces/kube/src/k8s.io/kubernetes/pkg/api
./register.go:74: cannot use unversioned.APIVersions literal (type *unversioned.APIVersions) as type runtime.Object in argument to Scheme.AddKnownTypes:
    *unversioned.APIVersions does not implement runtime.Object (missing IsAnAPIObject method)
./register.go:75: cannot use unversioned.APIGroupList literal (type *unversioned.APIGroupList) as type runtime.Object in argument to Scheme.AddKnownTypes:
    *unversioned.APIGroupList does not implement runtime.Object (missing IsAnAPIObject method)
./register.go:76: cannot use unversioned.APIGroup literal (type *unversioned.APIGroup) as type runtime.Object in argument to Scheme.AddKnownTypes:
    *unversioned.APIGroup does not implement runtime.Object (missing IsAnAPIObject method)
./register.go:77: cannot use unversioned.APIResourceList literal (type *unversioned.APIResourceList) as type runtime.Object in argument to Scheme.AddKnownTypes:
    *unversioned.APIResourceList does not implement runtime.Object (missing IsAnAPIObject method)
```

@pmorie @smarterclayton @liggitt  I'm not sure who to ask about this, but it seems like a pretty severe problem.
